121
00:11:32,090 --> 00:11:34,600
<i>saat kau bilang kau berhenti karena aku?</i>

122
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,020
<i>Guru...</i>

123
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:39,600
<i>Kau benar-benar telah banyak berubah.</i>

