130
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:12,160
Jangan jual ceritamu.

131
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:15,020
Kau mencoba mengubah pikiranku.

132
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:18,040
Kau hanya perlu tanda tanganku, kan?

133
